Author: Sinu John
www.sinujohn.wordpress.com

This project implements an Inverted Index which forms the backend of a Search Engine.
The Inverted Index is created in an HBase Table. Code that creates the index into a file is also present.
Look at the comments in IndexCreator.java
Dependencies: Hadoop and HBase

Usage:
hadoop jar /path/to/SearchEn.jar me.sinu.search.index.IndexCreator /path/to/input /path/to/output
Example: 
hadoop jar /home/bduser/test/SearchEn.jar me.sinu.search.index.IndexCreator /user/input /user/output